About Us
Barefoot Bay Golf Course is the premier centerpiece of Barefoot Bay Recreation District. The largest mobile home community in Florida. This challenging 18-hole executive course will test all player’s abilities. Renowned architect Joe Lee has used the beautiful landscapes and acreage to perfection. The small and challenging greens, along with the well protected approaches will test all your shot making ability. The course is 3,689 yards from the tips. It is a fantastic experience for seniors, juniors, women, or anybody who really needs to dial in their proximity shot making.  And yes, it doesn’t take 4 and 1/2 hours to play.
